title: Welcome to Unfiltered: The JBL Podcast
itunes:title: Welcome to Unfiltered: The JBL Podcast
description:
Ever wonder how groundbreakers, pioneers, and influencers, became so confident in who they are and what they do? Or maybe you’ve always admired how your favorite artist or musician seems so comfortable in their own skin and using their voice and art to express their identity. Wanna learn how they do it? Welcome to “Unfiltered: The JBL Podcast,” a brand new podcast from iHeart Radio in partnership with JBL. Every week, join host, singer and songwriter Betty Who, as she talks to the most creative and inspiring minds of today and learns how they found ways to be themselves, completely unfiltered. From music and art to high fashion and elite athletes, these young doers and disruptors tell us how they tune out the noise and reach the top of their game.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
